  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When you say there were no general stores in the sense what we used to know now, but they were-- there were shops which made quite lot of turnover during the season, during the thermal place season.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people who came there as guests from lot of European countries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even I remember English people came quite a lot because the thermal water was 80 degrees Celsius hot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was really helping for rheumatic people, suffering from rheumatism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were two or three other places, but Trenc Teplice-- I would say the second in the country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how long did your family stay in Trenc Tepla for?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The family-- as-- as a family, we were staying in Trenc Tepla till 1930 or '31 because my father was very ambitious and because of traveling so often to the capital town of Slovakia, where he purchased from the importers, we used to sell-- I have to mention it-- we used to sell, for instance, dates, bananas, oranges.",
      "word_count": 58
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was in the beginning of the 1920 and '25-- very unusual.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he knew very well, as a-- as a very ambitious business man, that this delicatessens which he sold are very important part of his business because the people used to come from the nearby thermal place and bought these things, or he delivered it to some of the smaller shops in the thermal place itself.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was very ambitious, and he went and bought things which the other shops didn't dare to buy.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he was financially so well off and his observing of the more [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] better life in the big cities.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
